}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== :The model on the package is '''F5U234v1'''.
'''CZ'''''11655451'' is the serial number of the hub populating this entry.
"F5U234 REV:2.4/1.6mm" is silkscreened on the board. :The '''Genesys Logic''' hub IC is marked with "GL852G", "MN3BA02G03", and "018SP14991". :The capacitors on the board are all from '''Canicon'''.
The power adapter included with the hub appears to be an ''unbranded'' PS0526 (100-240VAC ~ 50/60Hz, 0.5A -> 5VDC 2.5-2.6A).
